544
00:35:02,754 --> 00:35:04,631
l'm a bad father !

545
00:35:07,674 --> 00:35:09,505
l mean--

546
00:35:14,674 --> 00:35:17,142
l'm a bad father.

547
00:35:18,594 --> 00:35:22,792
