557
00:35:58,874 --> 00:36:00,705
Okay, 6:00.

558
00:36:00,794 --> 00:36:03,706
- Ten to six.
- All right.

559
00:36:03,754 --> 00:36:07,064
All right. But if l tell
Max that you're coming,

560
00:36:07,114 --> 00:36:10,265
