573
00:36:50,274 --> 00:36:52,947
- l would not like them--"
- Excuse me.

574
00:36:52,994 --> 00:36:57,226
Hi. l'm Max's bad father--
Er, l'm his father.

575
00:36:57,314 --> 00:37:01,466
- Dad !
