you made last night. lt came true, Max.

579
00:37:12,874 --> 00:37:15,786
- Really ? You mean you
have to tell the truth ?
- Yes.

580
00:37:15,874 --> 00:37:17,944
- No matter what ?
- No matter what !

581
00:37:17,994 --> 00:37:21,111
- ls wrestling real ?
- ln the Olympics, yes.
On channel 23, no.

582
00:37:21,154 --> 00:37:25,033
