a cow, it would have hurt her feelings.

596
00:38:09,314 --> 00:38:12,863
- Understand ?
- My teacher tells me
real beauty's on the inside.

597
00:38:12,954 --> 00:38:16,185
That's just something
ugly people say.

598
00:38:16,234 --> 00:38:19,943
Max, no one can survive
