my promotion, l could even lose my job.

600
00:38:23,874 --> 00:38:25,751
Now, l need your help, Max.

601
00:38:25,794 --> 00:38:28,069
[ Sighs ] Okay.

602
00:38:28,154 --> 00:38:32,193
