612
00:39:25,474 --> 00:39:27,305
And this time, mean it.

613
00:39:27,394 --> 00:39:29,749
- But l can't !
- Why not ?

614
00:39:29,794 --> 00:39:32,991
- 'Cause l don't want you to lie.
